Lila STEPHENS, as Administratrix of the Estate of Elwin Stephens, Deceased, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. REDMAN STEAMSHIP CORPORATION, Defendant-Appellee. No. 279. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 4, 1935. Simone N. Gazan, of New York City, for appellant. Kirlin, Campbell, Hickox, Keating & McGrann, of New York City (Vernon S. Jones and Walter X. Connor, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before MANTON, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
